{"TopicId":216223,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Dark mode code blocks are still unreadable","CreatedByName":"bigyihsuan","CreatedById":29291,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-04T20:58:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"bigyihsuan","CreatedById":29291,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-04T20:58:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m using the \u0022KSP Dark Red\u0022 theme. Code blocks are still not readable because of dark text on a dark background:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KcZMH8i.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002261.00\u0022 height=\u0022602\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KcZMH8i.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-04T20:58:48Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2023 08:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by bigyihsuan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tg626","CreatedById":112361,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-04T22:57:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EBlock of Code\n\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;h1\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EFooBar\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/h1\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;ul\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n  \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;li\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EThing 1\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/li\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n  \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;li\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EThing B\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/li\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/ul\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n\nEnd\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoesn\u0027t work for either \u0022dark\u0022 versions KSP or Red.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn other news, I just discovered we have Themes...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-04T22:58:32Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2023 10:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by tg626\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T13:12:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo whatever formatting the code block is adding overrules the default font colour- in this case the white text of dark mode(s). I\u2019m no UI expert but that doesn\u2019t seem \u003Ci\u003Etoo\u003C/i\u003E\u00A0difficult to fix\u2026\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bigyihsuan","CreatedById":29291,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-14T22:37:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/225122-dakota/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022225122\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/225122-dakota/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dakota\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0It has been several Mondays now \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0W\u003C/span\u003Ehen will this (admittedly minor issue that can be circumvented by using the light theme)\u00A0be fixed?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224265677\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022215861\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679814420\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225122\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dakota\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/26/2023 at 3:07 AM, Dakota said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeya, thanks for the heads-up. Will fix on Monday.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dakota","CreatedById":225122,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-14T22:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe I got this fixed. Had to do some css overrides in the theme backend, which was more difficult than I thought. Should be readable in both themes now. Feel free to follow-up some syntax highlighting is still messed up. Thanks for the ping \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/29291-bigyihsuan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002229291\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/29291-bigyihsuan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@bigyihsuan\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bigyihsuan","CreatedById":29291,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-15T01:00:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHooray, it\u0027s fixed! Thanks Dakota!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}